narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would summarize this as a chance to substantially grow in your abilities as a french student. There is a good bit of work but it was definitely worth it for me
Readings are not that great, but if you can take a class with Mme Charney, definitely do.
I would reccomend French 151 to anyone wanting to perfect their writing and grammar.
